OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FFormer mayor of Liverpool Joe Anderson
OL,7,Fhas appeared in court accused of
OL,8,Finvolvement in council corruption.
OL,10,FAnderson, 67, was one of 12 people
OL,11,Fcharged as part of Operation Aloft,
OL,12,Flaunched by police to look into the
OL,13,Fawarding of commercial and business
OL,14,Fcontracts from Liverpool City Council
OL,15,Fbetween 2010 and 2020.
