OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FHe indicated not guilty pleas to
OL,7,Fcharges of bribery, misconduct in a
OL,8,Fpublic office and conspiracy to commit
OL,9,Fmisconduct in a public office, at
OL,10,FPreston Magistrates' Court on Friday
OL,11,F28 March.
OL,13,FOn the misconduct charge, he is said
OL,14,Fto have sent and/or arranged to have
OL,15,Fsent "threatening letters" to himself.
OL,17,FThe ex-social worker, of Knotty Ash in
OL,18,FLiverpool, was elected mayor of the
OL,19,Fcity from the time the role was
OL,20,Fcreated in 2012 until 2021.
