OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FPreviously in a statement posted on
OL,7,Fsocial media site X, he said: "I am
OL,8,Finnocent of charges and will fight to
OL,9,Fclear my name."
OL,11,FHis son David Anderson, 37, of
OL,12,FWavertree, faces a charge with
OL,13,Fconspiracy to commit misconduct in a
OL,14,Fpublic office which he denies.
OL,16,FAlso attending court was Derek Hatton,
OL,17,F77, who was deputy leader of Liverpool
OL,18,FCity Council in the 1980s, and a
OL,19,Fformer director and assistant director
OL,20,Fat the local authority.
