OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FHis wife Sonjia Hatton, 49, of
OL,7,FAigburth, indicated a not guilty plea
OL,8,Fto one count of misconduct in a public
OL,9,Foffice by providing and seeking
OL,10,Fconfidential council information over
OL,11,Fmatters of commercial and business use
OL,12,Fto Mr Hatton's contacts and to his
OL,13,Fbusiness dealings.
OL,15,FAndrew Barr, formerly the council's
OL,16,Fassistant director of highways and
OL,17,Fplanning, 51, of Ainsdale, Merseyside,
OL,18,Fis charged with conspiracy to commit
OL,19,Fmisconduct in a public office and also
OL,20,Fa charge of bribery for which he
OL,21,Findicated a not guilty plea.
